  "detailed_description": "“Portal Box” is a puzzle game that combines portals with box-pushing mechanics. In this game, you’ll use portals to solve seemingly impossible puzzles. As you progress, you’ll learn about the intricacies of portal mechanics and apply that knowledge to your decryption challenges. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891210/extras/97bf8790af412fa328fdeb077c87a3c5.poster.avif?t=1731933477\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891210/extras/97bf8790af412fa328fdeb077c87a3c5.webm?t=1731933477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891210/extras/97bf8790af412fa328fdeb077c87a3c5.mp4?t=1731933477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With over a 100 handcrafted puzzles, “Portal Box” offers a gradual learning curve, allowing you to explore the fascinating interaction between boxes and portals.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891210/extras/25c4faf0e56119b8f05c17fe2dbce2be.poster.avif?t=1731933477\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891210/extras/25c4faf0e56119b8f05c17fe2dbce2be.webm?t=1731933477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891210/extras/25c4faf0e56119b8f05c17fe2dbce2be.mp4?t=1731933477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
